==当前可用微格式==

===Geo===
[[Geo|Geo]] 用来标记地理坐标（经度和纬度）。

Geo 可以被索引(例如"寻找距离X地点2公里范围内的所有地点")，在其他网站上看这个地点，或者为 GPS 等设备提供支持。 

维基百科上所有的地点性质的条目都应该使用。

在维基百科上，{{tl|coord}} 将 Geo 格式应用到坐标上。 它被设计用来替换 coor 模板家族，简化数据条目。

请参考：
*the [[Wikipedia:WikiProject_Geographical_coordinates|Geographical coordinates Project]]
**[[Wikipedia:WikiProject_Geographical_coordinates#Articles_with_coordinates,_but_not_linked_to_Template:Coor|Articles with coordinates; not linked to Template:Coor]]

====维基百科上的 Geo 举例====

'''参考 [[:Category:經緯模板|:Category:經緯模板]]'''

举例:

*[[Geo_(microformat)#Example|Geo (microformat)#Example]]
*All of the <!-- many thousands of--> articles using {{[[:template:coord|:template:coord]]}} <!-- or any of the "coor" family of templates which it supersedes-->. Examples:
**Most of the articles in [[:Category:Lists_of_coordinates|:Category:Lists of coordinates]]
**[[Great_Barr|Great Barr]] <!-- [[Hamstead_railway_station|Hamstead railway station]], [[Belfast|Belfast]], [[Ridge_Route|Ridge Route]] -->
**{{tl|Geolinks-AUS-suburbscale}}
*[[Template:GeoTemplate|GeoTemplate]], which is called by '''many thousands''' of other Wikipedia pages.
**Example: the coordinates (top right) in [[Great_Barr|Great Barr]] link to [http://tools.wikimedia.de/~magnus/geo/geohack.php?params=52.54833_N_1.93212_W_region:GB_source:enwiki-osgb36(SP047945) a list of maps for Great Barr]; the latter now has a Geo microformat.
*在 hCard 数据中使用 Geo 的条目列表：
**[[Manchester_Ship_Canal#Coordinates|Manchester Ship Canal]]
**[[Netherton_Tunnel_Branch_Canal|Netherton Tunnel Branch Canal]]
*[[Robert_Baden-Powell,_1st_Baron_Baden-Powell|Robert Baden-Powell, 1st Baron Baden-Powell]] '''Featured Article''' uses {{tl|coord}}, both "title" and "inline".

====拓展====
There are three active proposals, none mutually-exclusive, and all backwards-compatible, to extend the geo microformat:
* [http://microformats.org/wiki/geo-extension-strawman geo-extension] - for representing coordinates on other planets, moons etc., and with non-WSG84 schema
**Of use for [[Template:Lunar_crater_data|Template:Lunar crater data]]
* [http://microformats.org/wiki/geo-elevation-examples geo-elevation] - for representing altitude
* [http://microformats.org/wiki/geo-waypoint-examples geo-waypoint] - for representing routes and boundaries, using waypoints

===hCard===
[[:en:hCard|:en:hCard]]可以提供人物 (人物条目和用户属性), 组织和地点的详细信息。

See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject_Microformats/hcard|Wikipedia:WikiProject Microformats/hcard]] for more.

*[http://hcard.geekhood.net/ 测试工具]

===hCalendar===

[[:en:hCalendar|:en:hCalendar]]则是提供事件的信息，可以直接把这些信息添加到日历、日程表或网站上。

维基百科上的历史上的今天栏目，新闻动态栏目应该会用的上（电视剧或电视节目?）


===hAtom===
[http://microformats.org/wiki/hatom hAtom] is for making feeds.

===hReview===
[[hReview|hReview]] is for marking up reviews, and could be used by, for example, [[:Template:Infobox_Album|:Template:Infobox Album]].

===Other===
*[http://microformats.org/wiki/rel-tag rel-tag]
*[[XHTML_Friends_Network|XFN]]
*[http://microformats.org/wiki/hresume hResume]

